JOSEPH ALLEN
. The prisoner came to my employer's shop, (William Blissett, No. 13, Middle-row, Holborn
) - he took a hat and went away with it - I pursued him and took him with it in his possession in the City, opposite Fox-court, within the bars - I saw him take the hat; I pursued and never lost sight of him - I gave the hat to the officer.

